{"tid":1646504,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我屌晒你地老母一個帶口罩嘅人都冇阿","createTime":"2019-10-11T10:22:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T10:27:00.000Z","uid":31020,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5330b4c1de280f095253b08721d5a75bf01acd68","tid":1646504,"uid":31020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:22:19.000Z","msg":"喂，帶個口罩好撚柒難？<br />\n我番放工左成個星期，三十個都係得一個有帶<br />\n今日仲離譜到一個都見唔到阿！！<br />\n<br />\n帶個口罩唔犯法架<br />\n又話全民口罩<br />\n點解好似得我一個咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n求下你地啦，口罩呢個真係基本野<br />\n又唔洗驚又唔洗流血又唔會比人拉<br />\n<br />\n口罩都唔難點反抗阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定大家已經接受左蒙面法喇？"},{"pid":"eea27e57fa5c5d8166be6075c2caa0d9b51dea4e","tid":1646504,"uid":31020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:22:40.000Z","msg":"口罩好難咩"},{"pid":"114a944d35cbc96bd8cd1034616430c95f454db7","tid":1646504,"uid":31020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:23:24.000Z","msg":"我每日都戴口罩返工放工 我依家放住工喊撚住咁打呢篇野<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1641534\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1641534</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"05d454fbe2477090267add36ede167f58a9c8c36","tid":1646504,"uid":31020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:24:17.000Z","msg":"教你四個步驟就可以做到全民口罩<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1637130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1637130</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我已經日日出post再twit<br />\n都係冇人阿<br />\n大家到底有冇做野？"},{"pid":"5a1707c35e89db32289b48489bf7ae8c66d99c45","tid":1646504,"uid":31020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:27:00.000Z","msg":"其實日日番工放工都帶個口罩<br />\n番到公司學校咪除左佢囉<br />\n其實帶個口罩真係好basic<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}